<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>Bb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Jesuh ca atu tho tuah, Vailam ralkap vialte, Ngiatnak puan kha va lek
 tuah, I teiter hin hlah u, Thawnnak in an tei dih tiang, Ralkap a hruai
 hna lai, Ral dihlak an tei tikah, Bawibik a si ngaingai.

[V2]
 Jesuh ca atu tho tuah, Muko thawng kha ngai tuah, Amah ral kha va do
 u, Nihin tho law kal tuah, Ral tam hmanhseh phang hlah u, Zaangthawnnak
 in tei u, Zaang thawngmi nan si caah, Ral tam nain tho u.

[V3]
 Jesuh ca atu tho tuah, Amah thawng lawng tein, Nan zaang nan bochan
 ahcun, Nan sungh lai kha ruat ko, Darphaw, Pathian thawngtha kha, Vaa
 chon law thlacam tuah, Kahnak rian a um caah, Jesuh ca i tim u.

[V4]
 Jesuh ca atu tho tuah, Dohnak a sau lai lo, Nihin dohnak thawng nan
 theih, Thaizing thannak si ko, Ral a teimi vialte nih, Sui luchin nan
 hmuh lai, Nannih nan Bawi Jesuh he, A zungzal nan nung lai.</lyrics>
<title>JESUH CA THO TUAH CH293</title>
<hymn_number>293</hymn_number>
</song>